  (str ministry) (str `Ministry of Information and Broadcasting`)
  (str department) (undefined)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to provide for the establishment of a Broadcasting Corporation for India, to be known as Prasar Bharati, to define its composition, functions and powers and to provide for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`)
